\c 14
\s Isipho sokuprofetha sidlula esokukhuluma ngendimi
\p
\v 1 Landelani uthando\x + 16.14.\x*; lifise\x + 12.31.\x* kakhulu \add izipho\add* zomoya\x + 12.1.\x*, kodwa ikakhulu ukuthi liprofethe\x + 11.4.\x*.
\v 2 Ngoba okhuluma ngendimi\x + Seb. 2.4.\x* kakhulumi ebantwini, kodwa kuNkulunkulu; ngoba kakho ozwayo\x + Gen. 11.7; 42.23.\x*, kanti ukhuluma izimfihlo ngomoya.
\v 3 Kodwa oprofethayo\x + 11.4.\x* ukhuluma ebantwini ukwakha\x + Roma 14.19.\x* lenkuthazo\x + 14.31. Seb. 13.15.\x* lenduduzo.
\v 4 Okhuluma ngendimi uyazakha yena, kodwa oprofethayo\x + 11.4.\x* wakha ibandla\x + 14.17. Seb. 9.31.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo ngiyathanda ukuthi lonke likhulume ngendimi\x + Seb. 2.4.\x*, kodwa\x + Nani 11.29.\x* kakhulu ukuthi liprofethe\x + 11.4.\x*; ngoba oprofethayo mkhulu kulokhuluma ngendimi, ngaphandle kokuthi atolike\x + 14.13.\x*, ukuze ibandla lemukele ukwakhiwa.
\p
\v 6 Khathesi-ke, bazalwane, uba ngifika kini ngikhuluma ngendimi, ngizalisiza ngani, nxa ngingakhulumi kini kumbe ekwembulelweni\x + 14.26. Efe. 1.17. Fil. 3.15.\x*, loba ekwazini\x + 12.8.\x*, loba kusiprofetho\x + 11.4.\x*, kumbe emfundisweni\x + 14.26. Seb. 2.42. Roma 6.17. Heb. 13.9.\x*?
\v 7 Ngokunjalo izinto ezingelampilo ezikhalayo, loba umhlanga, loba ichacho, uba zinganiki umehluko ngokukhala\x + Roma 10.18.\x*, kuzakwaziwa njani okuvuthelwayo ngomhlanga kumbe okutshaywayo ngomqangala?
\v 8 Ngoba-ke nxa uphondo lunika\x + Nani 10.1,9. Isa. 58.1. Jow. 2.1.\x* ukukhala okungaqondakaliyo, ngubani ozazilungisela impi\x + Isam. 9.9; 20.8.\x*?
\v 9 Kunjalo lani, uba linganiki inkulumo ecacileyo ngolimi, kuzakwaziwa njani okukhulunywayo? Ngoba lizakuba likhuluma emoyeni\x + 9.26.\x*.
\v 10 Kukhona, nxa kungenzakala\x + 15.37.\x*, imihlobo eminengi kangaka yemisindo\x + Luka 15.29. Joha. 12.37.\x*\x + 12.28.\x* emhlabeni kodwa kawukho ongatsho lutho;
\v 11 ngakho uba ngingawazi umqondo welizwi, ngizakuba ngowezizweni\x + Seb. 28.2.\x* kulowo okhulumayo, lalowo okhulumayo \add uzakuba\add* ngowezizweni kimi.
\v 12 Kunjalo lani, lokhu litshisekela \add izipho\add* zomoya, dingani ukuthi livame ekwakhiweni\x + Roma 14.19.\x* kwebandla.
\p
\v 13 Ngakho-ke okhulumayo ngendimi\x + Seb. 2.4.\x* kakhuleke ukuthi atolike\x + 14.13.\x*.
\v 14 Ngoba uba ngikhuleka ngendimi, umoya wami uyakhuleka, kodwa ingqondo yami kayilasithelo.
\v 15 Ngakho kuyini? Ngizakhuleka ngomoya, njalo ngizakhuleka langengqondo; ngizahlabelela indumiso\x + Efe. 5.19. Kol. 3.16.\x* ngomoya, njalo ngizahlabelela indumiso langengqondo\x + Hlab. 47.7.\x*.
\v 16 Uba kungenjalo, nxa ubonga ngomoya\x + 10.16.\x*, lowo ogcwalisa indawo yongafundanga\x + 14.23,24. Seb. 4.13.\x* uzamutsho njani uAmeni\x + Neh. 5.13. & Isam. 5.14.\x* ekubongeni kwakho\x + 11.24.\x*, lokhu engakwazi okutshoyo?
\v 17 Ngoba isibili wena ubonga kuhle\x + 11.24.\x*, kodwa omunye kakhiwa.
\v 18 Ngiyambonga uNkulunkulu wami ukuthi ngikhuluma ngendimi\x + Neh. 5.13. & Isam. 5.14.\x* kakhulu kulani lonke;
\v 19 kodwa ebandleni ngithanda ukukhuluma amazwi amahlanu ngengqondo yami, ukuze ngifundise labanye\x + Luka 1.4.\x*, kulamazwi ayizinkulungwane ezilitshumi ngendimi.
\p
\v 20 Bazalwane, lingabi ngabantwana engqondweni\x + Efe. 4.14. Heb. 5.12,13.\x*; kodwa ebubini banini zingane\x + 3.1. Mat. 11.25. Roma 16.19. Mat. 18.3.\x*, lekunakaneni libe ngabakhulileyo.
\v 21 Emlayweni\x + Roma 3.19. Joha. 10.34.\x* kulotshiwe ukuthi: Ngezinye indimi\x + Isa. 28.11,12. Dute. 28.49.\x* langezinye indebe ngizakhuluma lalesisizwe, langokunjalo labo kabayikungizwa, itsho iNkosi.
\v 22 Ngakho indimi zingezesibonakaliso, kungeyisikho kwabakholwayo, kodwa kwabangakholwayo; kanti isiprofetho\x + 11.4.\x*, kungayi\add siso\add* sabangakholwayo, kodwa sabakholwayo.
\v 23 Ngakho uba ibandla lonke libuthene ndawonye, labo bonke bakhulume ngendimi, besekungena abangafundanga\x + 14.23,24. Seb. 4.13.\x* loba abangakholwayo, kabazukuthi liyahlanya yini\x + Seb. 2.13.\x*?
\v 24 Kodwa uba bonke beprofetha\x + 11.4.\x*, njalo kungene othile ongakholwayo loba ongafundanga\x + 14.23,24. Seb. 4.13.\x*, uyakhuzwa\x + Joha. 16.8.\x* yibo bonke, ahlolwe yibo bonke,
\v 25 langokunjalo izinto ezifihliweyo zenhliziyo yakhe ziyadalulwa; ngokunjalo uzakuwa ngobuso\x + Luka 17.16. Mat. 17.6. Luka 5.12.\x* akhonze uNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 5.16.\x*, ebika ukuthi uNkulunkulu ngoqotho uphakathi kwenu\x + Isa. 45.14. Zek. 8.23.\x*.
\s Indlela yokukhonza kwebandla
\p
\v 26 Ngakho kuyini, bazalwane? Loba nini libuthana, ngulowo lalowo wenu elesihlabelelo\x + Efe. 5.19.\x*, elemfundiso\x + 14.6.\x*, elolimi\x + 12.10.\x*, elesambulelo\x + 14.6.\x*, elokutolika\x + 12.10.\x*. Konke kakwenzelwe ekwakheni\x + 12.7. 2 Kor. 12.19; 13.10. Efe. 4.12. Roma 14.19.\x*.
\v 27 Uba umuntu ekhuluma ngendimi\x + 12.10.\x*, \add kakube\add* ngababili, kumbe bangadluli kwabathathu, njalo \add ba\add*dedelane, lomunye katolike;
\v 28 kodwa uba kungekho umtoliki, kumele athule ebandleni; akhulume kuye ngokwakhe lakuNkulunkulu.
\v 29 Abaprofethi-ke\x + 14.32,37. 14.1,16,31. Seb. 11.27.\x* ababili loba abathathu kabakhulume, labanye kabahlolisise\x + 6.5; 11.31. 12.10.\x*.
\v 30 Kodwa uba kusembulwa komunye ohleziyo, kathule owokuqala\x + 1 Thes. 5.19,20.\x*.
\v 31 Ngoba lonke lingaprofetha\x + 11.4.\x* munye ngamunye, ukuze bonke bafunde, njalo bonke bakhuthazwe\x + 14.3.\x*;
\v 32 lemimoya yabaprofethi\x + 14.32,37. 14.1,16,31. Seb. 11.27.\x* iyathotshiselwa abaprofethi.
\v 33 Ngoba uNkulunkulu kayisuye owesiphithiphithi, kodwa ngowokuthula, njengemabandleni\x + 7.17.\x* wonke abangcwele.
\v 34 Abesifazana\x + 1 Tim. 2.11,12.\x* benu kabathule emabandleni; ngoba kabavunyelwa\x + 1 Tim. 2.11,12.\x* ukukhuluma, kodwa ukuzithoba\x + 7.19. 1 Tim. 4.3. Dute. 4.12.\x*, njengoba lawo umlayo\x + Gen. 3.16.\x* usitsho.
\v 35 Uba-ke bethanda ukufunda ulutho, kababuze kubomkabo ekhaya; ngoba kulihlazo kowesifazana ukukhuluma ebandleni.
\v 36 Kumbe ilizwi likaNkulunkulu laphuma kini? Kumbe lafika kini lodwa yini?
\p
\v 37 Uba umuntu ecabanga\x + 11.16.\x* ukuthi ungumprofethi loba ungowomoya, umele ukwemukela\x + 2 Kor. 10.7. 1 Joha. 4.6.\x* izinto engilibhalela zona, ukuthi ziyimilayo yeNkosi;
\v 38 uba umuntu engazi, kumele engazi.
\v 39 Ngakho, bazalwane, tshisekelani\x + 12.31.\x* ukuprofetha\x + 13.8.\x*, njalo lingakuvimbeli ukukhuluma ngendimi\x + 13.8.\x*;
\v 40 konke\x + 14.33.\x* kakwenziwe ngemfanelo langokulandelana\x + Roma 13.13.\x*.
